{"title":"拖拉机就要开过来了","authors":["未央"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机就要开过来了\t未央"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走了千年的小路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年来加宽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种了千年的梯田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年整平坦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么来加宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么整平坦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为拖拉机就要开过来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为机械化就要实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青的小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一担两座山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的姑娘们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌喉赛琴弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么干劲冲天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么心似蜜甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为拖拉机就要开过来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为机械化就要实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走了千年的小路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年来加宽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种了千年的梯田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年整平坦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么来加宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么整平坦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为要走向社会主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为要修建幸福家园！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧！插秧的季节柳条没发绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种谷没下泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们忙着练插秧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采来松针作练习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年插秧用双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年插秧使机器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年插秧蔸蔸栽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年插秧垅垅推。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春水泛银波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风拂面吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插秧机滚滚过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一床绿毯铺在地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早练到晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮起来还不归。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已学好了啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里着了迷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，来吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插秧的季节；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，来吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫叫人等得心碎……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}